  "prompt": "What would be the Wipro joining dates for campus placed 2017 batch?",
  "response": "The joining dates for the Wipro 2017 batch, like for most companies, would have varied depending on several factors, such as the specific project, team, and location a candidate was assigned to. However, typically, Wipro and other IT companies in India often onboard freshers in batches, with common onboarding periods being in:\n\n1. **June-July**: For candidates who completed their degrees in April-May.\n2. **December-January**: For those who completed their degrees later in the year or for additional batches.\n\nIf you were part of the 2017 batch and are looking for an exact date, I would recommend checking any communication (emails, offer letters, etc.) you received from Wipro at that time. If you\u2019re asking for historical or reference purposes, you might need to contact Wipro\u2019s HR for specific details, as this would not be publicly available.",
